vlc-discordrpc-plugin (1.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Release version 1.2.0.
  * The static Rich Presence has been replaced with a user-customizable Rich
    Presence using tokens.
  * In addition, several internal bugs were fixed.

 -- Zukaritasu <zukaritasu@gmail.com>  Sat, 04 Apr 2026 12:12:00 -0400

vlc-discordrpc-plugin (1.1.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Release version 1.1.0.
  * The plugin now displays the playlist (by default, it is disabled).
  * The presence type has also been changed to Playing, Listening, and Watching,
    depending on the type of multimedia content.

 -- Zukaritasu <zukaritasu@gmail.com>  Mon, 06 Mar 2026 21:21:00 -0400

vlc-discordrpc-plugin (1.0.0-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Release version 1.0.0.
  * Provides integration between VLC Media Player and Discord.
  * Built with CMake, installs plugin into /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/vlc/plugins/misc/.

 -- Zukaritasu <zukaritasu@gmail.com>  Mon, 17 Feb 2026 21:19:00 -0400

vlc-discordrpc-plugin (1.0.0~beta1-1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Release version 1.0.0-beta1.
  * Provides integration between VLC Media Player and Discord.
  * Built with CMake, installs plugin into /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/vlc/plugins/misc/.

 -- Zukaritasu <zukaritasu@gmail.com>  Mon, 16 Feb 2026 02:05:00 -0400
